FBIS3-50525 "drlat002_k_94002" FBIS-LAT-94-002 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Jan 1994 SOUTH AMERICA Argentina New Defense Ministry Under Secretaries Installed PY0301224294 Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS in Spanish 2111 GMT 3 Jan 94 PY0301224294 Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] Buenos Aires, 3 Jan (NA) -- Jorge Baeza, the Defense Ministry's new military affairs secretary, today installed Ricardo Lagorio as policy and strategy under secretary and Roberto Ahumada as institutional affairs under secretary. Thus Lagorio and Ahumada succeed Virgilio Beltran and Eduardo De Simone, whose resignations were accepted by the Executive Branch. Defense Ministry Planning Secretary Guillermo Etchechoury and ministry departmental directors participated in the ceremony.
